#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:607
msgid "DEPTH_PRIORITY"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:613
msgid ""
"An integer that is used to adjust the :attr:`~scrapy.Request.priority` of a :"
"class:`~scrapy.Request` based on its depth."
