msgid ""
"The files that this class generates in the :ref:`job directory <job-dir>` "
"are an implementation detail, and may change without a warning in a future "
"version of Scrapy. Do not rely on the following information for anything "
"other than debugging purposes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../scrapy/dupefilters.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.dupefilters.RFPDupeFilter:14
